  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to determine the impact of sociocognitive and emotional factors on the time
      of the initial consult
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      identify wich sociocognitive factors influence the delay to go to a doctor after the
      emergence of first symptoms
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
