  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age ≥ 18 years

          -  oral cavity cancer, oropharynx cancer, hypopharynx cancer, larynx cancer

          -  non treated cancer

          -  patient informed of his diagnosis

          -  speak fluent french

          -  patient covered by health insurance

          -  signed informed consent

        Inclusion Criteria for &quot;interviewed &quot; patients :

          -  no speech troubles

          -  patient consents being recorded

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  history of cancer

          -  psychological history

          -  patient under guardianship
      </textblock>
